Statement of synthetic origin
-----------------------------
This dataset is **fully synthetic**. It was generated from a
deterministic statistical model documented in thesis Annex B Table 3
with `numpy.random.seed(42)`. It contains no references to real persons,
flights, operators, or incidents. It carries no special-category data
under GDPR Article 9 or KVKK Article 6.

The anonymized variant (`synthetic_n1179_anon.json`) has additionally
been processed through k-Anonymity (k=5) and Laplace differential
privacy (epsilon=1.0).

